OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA fine
OL,6,Fevening with plenty of late sunshine.
OL,7,FSome patchy low cloud and mist
OL,8,Fdeveloping overnight, especially over
OL,9,Fthe hills, but most remaining clear.
OL,10,FTurning chilly in the countryside.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAny early mist and low
OL,13,Fcloud quickly clearing leaving a fine
OL,14,Fand sunny day. Lighter winds for most
OL,15,Fallowing it to feel a little warmer.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
