OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FRemaining dry, sunny and warm on
OL,7,FThursday. Sunshine turning
OL,8,Fincreasingly hazy on Friday but
OL,9,Fremaining warm and increasingly humid.
OL,10,FFresher on Saturday with showers
OL,11,Fpossible.
